# Corvus Project Rules

## Build System

Always use `stack` for building and testing, not `cabal`.
Stack is located at `${HOME}/.local/bin/stack`:

- Build: `${HOME}/.local/bin/stack build`
- Test: `${HOME}/.local/bin/stack test`
- Run executables: `${HOME}/.local/bin/stack exec corvus` or `${HOME}/.local/bin/stack exec crv`
- REPL: `${HOME}/.local/bin/stack ghci`

## Code Style

- Use `ormolu` for code formatting
- Run `hlint` for linting (located at `${HOME}/.local/bin/hlint`)
